This project uses MIT-only licensing. Many Rust ecosystem crates are dual-licensed
under "MIT OR Apache-2.0" which allows us to use them under MIT terms:

Core Dependencies:
- candle-core, candle-nn, candle-transformers (Hugging Face Candle)
- cubecl, cubecl-cuda, cubecl-* (Tracel AI CubeCL GPU framework)
- tokenizers (Hugging Face Tokenizers)
- serde, serde_json, serde_yaml
- thiserror, anyhow
- tracing, tracing-subscriber

All such dependencies are used under MIT license terms.

