MPL-2.0 (Mozilla Public License):
- File-level copyleft: Only modifications to MPL-licensed files need MPL distribution
- Does NOT require releasing our MIT code under MPL
- option-ext is used as-is without modifications
- This notice satisfies MPL attribution requirements

MIT License:
- All direct dependencies and our code use MIT (permissive, no copyleft)
- Allows commercial use, modification, distribution with attribution

CUDA Toolkit Components:
- NVIDIA CUDA Toolkit used for GPU acceleration
- CUDA license allows development of applications
- Runtime requires NVIDIA drivers (proprietary)
- Our code interfaces via standard APIs (cubecl, candle)

